Package: OSCAUtils
Version: 0.0.2
Title: Utilities to Compile the OSCA Book
Authors@R:
    person("Aaron", "Lun", email="infinite.monkeys.with.keyboards@gmail.com", role=c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Provides specific utilities to compile the 
    "Orchestrating Single Cell Analysis" book. This includes
    Javascript and HTML chunk generators, setting of highly
    custom knitr options, and so on. It is not intended for
    any use other than book compilation.
